alt="Text Box: Top-Left: Two shiftable layers of CMY color filter arrays (CFAs) and their effective combination (bottom most layers). The combination is (a) CMY CFA before shift, (b) RGB CFA after a horizontal shift, (c) RGBCMY after a diagonal shift. Top-Right: Our prototype camera that can switch between RGB and CMY modes using a mechanical shift. Bottom-left: Our prototype camera that can switch between LDR and HDR modes using the same concept. Bottom-right: Images captured with the camera in LDR and HDR modes; the higher dynamic range achieved at the price of sacrificed resolution."><br
